transcript:
Executive: Sir, main kahin abhi busy hoon, main kar lunga sir woh jaise aap samjha rahe hain.
Customer: I know Sandeep sir aap kar lijiyega par itna bolna tha woh feedback aaya tha woh close kar raha hoon sir isiliye bas call kiya. 
Executive: Feedback kuch nahi aaya sir mere paas. Aayega toh main apne aap. 
Customer: Nahi nahi aapke paas nahi hai. Aapke paas nahi sir mere paas jo feedback aaya tha aapka woh aap khud se connect kar lenge. 
Executive: Jab mera kaam hi nahi hua toh close karke kya fayda hoga?
